snippet.title: My first game teaser
snippet.description:
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2797730/The_Overnight_Watch/

The first look at our game The Overnight Watch. Developed by Kyle Horwood who also made Security Booth. I'm extremely excited to finally show it off to everyone.
